%p{style: "margin:0 0 6px;font-size:15px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;"}
  Hello #{@resource.email}!
%p{style: "margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;"} Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.
%table{width: "100%", cellpadding: "0", cellspacing: "0", border: "0", style: "margin:8px 0 24px;"}
  %tr
    %td{align: "center"}
      %a{href: edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: "display:inline-block;padding:11px 28px;background-color:#4a5e82;color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;"}
        Change my password
%p{style: "margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#8b95a5;line-height:1.6;"} If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
%p{style: "margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#8b95a5;line-height:1.6;"} Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
